%pyspark

# Calculate deltas by time

orderColumns = ['Province_State', 'Last_Update']

jhuUSReportsDf = jhuUSReportsDf.orderBy(*orderColumns, ascending=True)
jhuUSReportsDf.filter(jhuUSReportsDf.Province_State == 'Maryland').select(jhuUSReportsDf.Province_State, jhuUSReportsDf.Last_Update).show(5)

stateDayWindow = Window.partitionBy("Province_State").orderBy("Last_Update")

# setup confirmed deltas
jhuUSReportsDf = jhuUSReportsDf.withColumn("prevVal", f.lag(jhuUSReportsDf.Confirmed).over(stateDayWindow))
jhuUSReportsDf = jhuUSReportsDf.withColumn("ConfirmedDelta", f.when(f.isnull(jhuUSReportsDf.Confirmed - jhuUSReportsDf.prevVal), 0).otherwise(jhuUSReportsDf.Confirmed - jhuUSReportsDf.prevVal))

# setup recovered deltas
jhuUSReportsDf = jhuUSReportsDf.withColumn("prevVal", f.lag(jhuUSReportsDf.Recovered).over(stateDayWindow))
jhuUSReportsDf = jhuUSReportsDf.withColumn("RecoveredDelta", f.when(f.isnull(jhuUSReportsDf.Recovered - jhuUSReportsDf.prevVal), 0).otherwise(jhuUSReportsDf.Recovered - jhuUSReportsDf.prevVal))

# setup deaths deltas
jhuUSReportsDf = jhuUSReportsDf.withColumn("prevVal", f.lag(jhuUSReportsDf.Deaths).over(stateDayWindow))
jhuUSReportsDf = jhuUSReportsDf.withColumn("DeathsdDelta", f.when(f.isnull(jhuUSReportsDf.Deaths - jhuUSReportsDf.prevVal), 0).otherwise(jhuUSReportsDf.Deaths - jhuUSReportsDf.prevVal))

# setup active deltas
jhuUSReportsDf = jhuUSReportsDf.withColumn("prevVal", f.lag(jhuUSReportsDf.Active).over(stateDayWindow))
jhuUSReportsDf = jhuUSReportsDf.withColumn("ActiveDelta", f.when(f.isnull(jhuUSReportsDf.Active - jhuUSReportsDf.prevVal), 0).otherwise(jhuUSReportsDf.Active - jhuUSReportsDf.prevVal))


# setup people tested deltas
jhuUSReportsDf = jhuUSReportsDf.withColumn("prevVal", f.lag(jhuUSReportsDf.People_Tested).over(stateDayWindow))
jhuUSReportsDf = jhuUSReportsDf.withColumn("PeopleTestedDelta", f.when(f.isnull(jhuUSReportsDf.People_Tested - jhuUSReportsDf.prevVal), 0).otherwise(jhuUSReportsDf.People_Tested - jhuUSReportsDf.prevVal))

# setup people tested deltas
jhuUSReportsDf = jhuUSReportsDf.withColumn("prevVal", f.lag(jhuUSReportsDf.People_Hospitalized).over(stateDayWindow))
jhuUSReportsDf = jhuUSReportsDf.withColumn("PeopleHospitalizedDelta", f.when(f.isnull(jhuUSReportsDf.People_Hospitalized - jhuUSReportsDf.prevVal), 0).otherwise(jhuUSReportsDf.People_Hospitalized - jhuUSReportsDf.prevVal))

jhuUSReportsDf = jhuUSReportsDf.drop("prevVal")
